snippet.title: Total pinball 25 gameplay (+Editor)
snippet.description:
Other game by Stellar Stone but ball get stucked

Has hidden key
F1-Cameras
F3-Light on/off
F2-Turn ball camera on/off
Q and E-Zoom in and out
F11-Show fps
F12-Screenshot
